        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/bbce88/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-01-09T14:46:01.436Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>I love Signal and would be very happy to see it grow.</p>\n<p>I often want to invite my friends and noticed the feature is not that easy to find. Even though it’s not technically a setting, you have to go into settings and scroll to the bottom of the settings page.</p>\n<p>I think that more users would invite friends if there were an easy “invite friends” button in the contact list when you start a new message.</p>\n<p>I mean just below the “Find by Phone Number” button (which, btw, should have a button in its screen letting you pull from your contacts). I’ve added a screenshot below.</p>\n<p>These would make Signal grow naturally :) Which I would be happy to see.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/b/2b4aa9ee252f0fb6a7c2e850008e5e05c0b4e627.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/2b4aa9ee252f0fb6a7c2e850008e5e05c0b4e627\" title=\"unnamed\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/b/2b4aa9ee252f0fb6a7c2e850008e5e05c0b4e627_2_230x500.jpeg\" alt=\"unnamed\" data-base62-sha1=\"6aYuR0JfOz8esOUQ43nNRcz56Z1\" width=\"230\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/b/2b4aa9ee252f0fb6a7c2e850008e5e05c0b4e627_2_230x500.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/b/2b4aa9ee252f0fb6a7c2e850008e5e05c0b4e627_2_345x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/b/2b4aa9ee252f0fb6a7c2e850008e5e05c0b4e627_2_460x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"313132\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">unnamed</span><span class=\"informations\">1125×2436 146 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
