        "cooked": "<p>There is an “Invite to Signal” option at the bottom of that screen, at least on Android. It becomes more visible if you start typing a search that reduces the results that are shown in that list. You also get an option to invite to Signal if you use “Find by Phone Number” and search for someone who is not already a Signal user.</p>",
