        "id": 258539,
        "name": null,
        "username": "doublefelix921",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/bbce88/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-01-09T19:45:43.589Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I just checked. I found the button on iOS as well - but the process of finding it required scrolling through my 400 contacts to see it after “Z” and “+”. I was kind of surprised, like, nobody scrolls to the bottom of their contacts to look for additional functionality <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/sweat_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":sweat_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sweat_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>I think that if the button were under the “Find by Phone Number” button, this would spur growth in invitations to signal, which I’d be really glad about. I suppose that 99% of users haven’t found the button in its current location, but if it were visible alongside the other features, that number could be reduced to maybe 50%. Seems like a solid win at a reasonably low cost. I’d be interested to hear what you think.</p>\n<p>Here is the screenshot of the bottom of my contacts, where the button was found, on iOS. It is after the “other characters” section of contacts, which comes after “Z”.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/b/1/b1dbb59c891f969462945a5730438345c4e0725b.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/b1dbb59c891f969462945a5730438345c4e0725b\" title=\"87351\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/b/1/b1dbb59c891f969462945a5730438345c4e0725b_2_230x500.jpeg\" alt=\"87351\" data-base62-sha1=\"pnpeJ49rwIA3KjaaAhFyHomDeSD\" width=\"230\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/b/1/b1dbb59c891f969462945a5730438345c4e0725b_2_230x500.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/b/1/b1dbb59c891f969462945a5730438345c4e0725b_2_345x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/b/1/b1dbb59c891f969462945a5730438345c4e0725b_2_460x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"313132\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">87351</span><span class=\"informations\">1125×2436 186 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
